shortcut_awesomewm
===

awesomeWM
---
NOTE:
  - super === Windows key === mod4
  - awesome v4.1
  : v3.5에서는 동작하지 않는 단축키도 있음

# Window manager control
       super + Control + r
           Restart awesome.

       super + Shift + q
           Quit awesome.

super + r
   Run prompt.
   탭컴플리션, 단어지우기(<C-w>) 등 기본편집 기능존재

       super + x
           Run Lua code prompt.

super + Return
   Spawn terminal emulator.

super + s
   toggle help shortcut

       super + w
           Open main menu.

# Clients

## resize window
  - toggle full: super + m
  - toggle horizontal maxmum: shift + super + m
  - toggle vertial maxmum: ctrl + super + m

## move window move 
super + shift + <j|k>

## else
       super + n
           Minimize client.

       super + Control + n
           Restore client.

       super + f
           (toggle)Set client fullscreen.

super + Shift + c
   Kill focused client.

       super + t
           Set client on-top.

# Navigation
super + j
   Focus next client.

super + k
   Focus previous client.

       super + u
           Focus first urgent client.

super + Left
   View previous tag.

super + Right
   View next tag.

super + 1-9
   Switch to tag 1-9.

       super + Control + j
           Focus next screen.

       super + Control + k
           Focus previous screen.

super + Escape
   Focus previously selected tag set.
super + Tab
   Focus previously selected screen

# Layout modification
       super + Shift + j
           Switch client with next client.

       super + Shift + k
           Switch client with previous client.

       super + o
           Send client to next screen.

super + h
   Decrease master width factor by 5%.

super + l
   Increase master width factor by 5%.

       super + Shift + h
           Increase number of master windows by 1.

       super + Shift + l
           Decrease number of master windows by 1.

       super + Control + h
           Increase number of columns for non-master windows by 1.

       super + Control + l
           Decrease number of columns for non-master windows by 1.

       super + space
           Switch to next layout.

       super + Shift + space
           Switch to previous layout.

super + Control + space
   Toggle client floating status.

       super + Control + Return
           Swap focused client with master.

       super + Control + 1-9
           Toggle tag view.

super + Shift + 1-9
   Tag client with tag.
   스크린의 태그를 변경시킴

       super + Shift + Control + 1-9
           Toggle tag on client.

